OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,FEugeniusz Niedzielski, Age 100, Polish
OL,7,F1st Armoured Division
OL,9,FInterviewed 17 September 2023
OL,11,FDisplaced from his home in Poland
OL,12,Ffollowing both the German and Russian
OL,13,Finvasions, Mr Niedzielski became part
OL,14,Fof his country's exiled armed forces.
OL,16,FServing in the Middle East as an
OL,17,Finfantryman he was brought to England
OL,18,Fahead of D-Day to be retrained as a
OL,19,Fmotorbike, car and tank driver.
