OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,F"They took us to Southampton and we
OL,7,Flanded in Normandy in July. The first
OL,8,Fthing I saw was a Canadian jeep
OL,9,Fcarrying four injured soldiers. Red
OL,10,Fbandages and everything.
OL,12,F"I nearly fainted seeing those
OL,13,Fsoldiers laying there wounded.
OL,15,F"I was a spare driver and when we got
OL,16,Fto Normandy a driver got sick and they
OL,17,Fsent him back to England. And I got a
OL,18,Ftank, the tank I drove all the way
OL,19,Ffrom Normandy to Germany.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
