OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,F"I always called it the iron coffin
OL,7,Fbecause once I saw a Sherman tank
OL,8,Fdestroyed and the soldier tried to
OL,9,Fescape from the top and got machine
OL,10,Fgunned.
OL,12,F"He got caught by his legs, hanging
OL,13,Fdown. The legs were at the top and his
OL,14,Fhead was down."
