OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,FMr Niedzielski was in action in the
OL,7,Fdecisive engagement of the battle of
OL,8,FNormandy at the Falaise Gap - or
OL,9,Fpocket - in which the Allies encircled
OL,10,FGerman forces and captured thousands
OL,11,Fof enemy troops. He and his crew came
OL,12,Funder heavy attack at that time.
OL,14,F"Our commanding officer told us we
OL,15,Fwere the cork in the bottle because we
OL,16,Fclosed the German escape. We could see
OL,17,Fthem in the woods with anti tank guns.
OL,18,FA Panzer division. Terrible. Bullets
OL,19,Fflying everywhere. German scout cars
OL,20,Ftried to escape.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
