OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,F"There was a road to the bottom of the
OL,7,Fhill, and one morning a scout car came
OL,8,Falong and they caught them out anyway
OL,9,Fbecause there were soldiers everywhere
OL,10,Fon that hill.
OL,12,F"There were dead bodies and horses and
OL,13,Ftanks. Everything was laying there. It
OL,14,Fwas a German graveyard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
