OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Eugeniusz
OL,4,CNiedzielski
OL,6,F"And from there we started chasing all
OL,7,Fthe way through the west part of
OL,8,FFrance and down to Belgium. It was the
OL,9,FGerman retreat from Normandy, that is
OL,10,Fwhat it was. Our division took pride
OL,11,Fin it and it's never been mentioned
OL,12,Felsewhere. They don't mention it in
OL,13,FBritish history.
OL,15,F"We knew we would never return to
OL,16,FPoland because they had already signed
OL,17,Fthe partition for Poland before we
OL,18,Flanded in Normandy."
